pulses.name: 20240903 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
03 Sep 2024 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- China (CN): The most active source of attacks, primarily targeting vulnerabilities in various devices, including NETGEAR and D-Link, as well as leveraging the Mozi botnet.
- India (IN): Involved in multiple attacks, particularly exploiting vulnerabilities in GPON routers and utilizing the Mozi botnet.
- Egypt (EG): Active in various attacks, especially using the Mirai botnet and exploiting vulnerabilities in MVPower DVR devices.

https://www.linkedin.com/posts/starlightintel_cybersecurity-cyberattack-rce-activity-7236746085631717377-nxxV?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop
